title: Trendowjackets 1/10: Robert Durst, Yellowjackets, NBA, Clay Aiken, Sen. Scott Baldwin, The Golden Globes
itunes:title: Trendowjackets 1/10: Robert Durst, Yellowjackets, NBA, Clay Aiken, Sen. Scott Baldwin, The Golden Globes
description:
In this edition of Trendowjackets, Jack and Miles discuss beloved public figures Robert Durst AND Bob Saget passing away, the new show 'Yellowjackets', NBA news, Clay Aiken running for congress, Sen. Scott Baldwin saying teachers should be 'impartial' when teaching about Nazis, and the Golden Globes happening.
